","tag-generosity-al-karm","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-allah-names-asma-ul-husna","tag-purification-of-the-soul-tazkiyyat-al-nafs","tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-97Q","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":41912,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/05\/02\/allah-loves-cleanliness\/","url_meta":{"origin":35082,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Purity: Allah is clean and loves cleanliness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 2, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah is pure and He loves purity, He is clean and He loves cleanliness, He is noble and He loves nobility, and He is generous and He loves generosity, so clean your homes.\u201d Source: Musnad Abi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36562,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/03\/jawad-al-jud\/","url_meta":{"origin":35082,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jud: Allah is generous, magnanimous, righteous","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty is magnanimous and He loves magnanimity. He loves the highest morals and He detests pettiness.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 5\/28 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13450,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/08\/allah-is-noble\/","url_meta":{"origin":35082,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Karam: Allah is noble, He loves nobility","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is noble. He loves nobility and the highest morals, and He detests pettiness.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304\u00a020781 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13720,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/24\/barakah-enjoy-blessings-moderation\/","url_meta":{"origin":35082,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Blessings: Enjoy blessings of Allah in moderation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEat, drink, and give in charity. Wear nice clothing, but without pride or extravagance. Verily, Allah loves for His blessings to be seen upon His servants.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6708 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1622,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/27\/until-he-loves-for-people\/","url_meta":{"origin":35082,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Until he loves people as he loves himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone of you has faith until he loves for people what he loves for himself, and until he loves a person only for the sake of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 13875 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11819,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/allah-loves-see-blessings\/","url_meta":{"origin":35082,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Bounties: Allah loves to see His blessings on His servants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Zuhayr ibn Abi 'Alqamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty loves to see the traces of blessings on his servant. He does not love one who wallows in misery and pessimism.\" Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 5167 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064f\u0647\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35082","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=35082"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35082\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=35082"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=35082"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=35082"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}